body:
The python3 failure should be easy to fix:

```
packages/tensorflow/contrib/repeat/python/ops/repeat_op.py", line 50, in _RepeatGrad
    for i in xrange(axis):
NameError: name 'xrange' is not defined
```

You need to use `six.moves.xrange`.
